50|$|The CIRCM system, (along {{with the}} older LAIRCM and ATIRCM <b>systems)</b> provide a <b>directional</b> <b>infrared</b> <b>countermeasure,</b> which employs both threat-tracking capabilities, as well {{defensive}} measures employing modulating laser pulses to confuse missiles' guidance systems causing them to miss their target.|$|R
