50|$|BAE Systems' AN/ALQ-212 {{advanced}} threat <b>infrared</b> <b>countermeasures</b> (ATIRCM) - {{part of a}} directable <b>infrared</b> <b>countermeasures</b> suite - is fielded on U.S. Army CH-47 Chinook helicopters. The suite provides {{protection against}} an array of threats, including all infrared threat bands. The AN/ALQ-212 incorporates one or more infrared jam heads to counter multiple missile attacks.|$|R
